{"tid":410753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【殖民地黑警】盧偉聰：需要時尋求律政司意見   無「大細超」","createTime":"2017-09-23T08:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T10:14:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd273822532888c7355f2b40d86ebfef47b90412","tid":410753,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170923/s00001/bf0f83000f5ea380999aac6a55557dca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170923%2Fs00001%2Fbf0f83000f5ea380999aac6a55557dca.jpg&h=3d1773c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建制派立法會議員何君堯的「殺無赦」言論繼續發酵，警務處長盧偉聰表示，事件已交由港島總區刑事部跟進，暫有未有人被捕，有需要時會向律政司尋求意見。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰今早見傳媒時，未有透露案件調查進度。被問到過往有人發表威嚇性言論，警方迅速作出拘捕行動，是次是否「大細超」，盧偉聰否認，並指需要視乎現場環境有否合理懷疑有人違法，才能作出拘捕行動，強調警方會公平公正調查，有需要時會向律政師尋求意見。"},{"pid":"144a22e4504c1050ace48e59419bb9aa598e8ac8","tid":410753,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc53fa48f3ff0792e065c3c9da01e84b4ec590fd","tid":410753,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5678a82fb63190abc8f8b72bc3c7645fe5afe2c","tid":410753,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ae1d25260b76c04858aa7c7361eee668c8636f","tid":410753,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"朱鳩偉揾左幾耐法律意見？"},{"pid":"1df552a32f57d8b1b0a1f00f460169547249bb55","tid":410753,"uid":38572,"like":0